Class NewsItemComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.iisys.mmis.rssparser.NewsItemComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<NewsItem>

    public class NewsItemComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<NewsItem>
    The class NewsItemComparator provides a comparator for objects of class "NewsItem". For this purpose two items are compared by their publication date. With this approach the comparator facilitates the sorting of news item according to their publications date.
